PrecisEnactment of the NEW SUBSTANCES NOTIFICATION REGULATIONS which are designed to ensure that no new substances will be manufactured or imported on a commercial scale before an assessment has been carried out to determine the risk posed to the environment and human health, EFFECTIVE July 1, 1994.
